680
00:36:37,750 --> 00:36:41,083
AND WE'LL LET YOU KNOW WHEN
SOMETHING COMES UP.

681
00:36:41,250 --> 00:36:43,959
NOW EXCUSE ME, MA'AM.

682
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:52,417
