HOME BY CHRISTMAS.

764
00:41:31,166 --> 00:41:31,834
&gt;&gt; LILLY!

765
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:32,959
&gt;&gt; HE DO SOMETHING SERIOUS?

766
00:41:33,542 --> 00:41:37,333
&gt;&gt; HE WAS ARRESTED FOR HITTING
A MAN ON THE HEAD WITH A

767
00:41:37,500 --> 00:41:38,583
