DANGEROUS.

881
00:47:40,542 --> 00:47:44,500
THE BULLS ARE NASTY, AND NOT
EVERYBODY YOU MEET'S GONNA BE

882
00:47:44,667 --> 00:47:45,417
LIKE ME.

883
00:47:46,208 --> 00:47:49,041
THERE'S DANGEROUS PEOPLE
OUT THERE.

884
00:47:49,709 --> 00:47:53,750
